      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/dad562e4-c4ea-11e3-a54d-52540035b04c).  Ran 19 tests.  2 tests failed: sanity-lfsck, lustre-rsync-test.",
