        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2014-05-16 16:08:54.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nNow the Intel build system has been changed to avoid this option is it OK to proceed with this patch or would be still be better to accept this option but print a warning if it's given?\n\nThere have been other options removed in the past and the getopt line is fairly unwieldy so I'm in favour of removing it entirely.",
